oss) |<small>N/A</small> |- | December 7, 1991 || [[Rennes]] || [[France]] || Salle Omnisports (Trans Musicales) | Various Artists |- ! colspan="5" |North America |- | December 27, 1991 || [[Los Angeles]] || rowspan="9" | [[United States]] || [[Los Angeles Memorial Sports Arena]] | rowspan="5" |[[Pearl Jam]] & [[Red Hot Chili Peppers]] |- | December 28, 1991 || [[Del Mar, California|Del Mar]] || Pat O'Brien Pavilion, [[Del Mar Fairgrounds]] |- |December 29, 1991 |[[Tempe, Arizona]] |[[ASU Activity Center]] |- |December 31, 1991 |[[Daly City, California]] |[[Cow Palace]] |- |January 2, 1992 |[[Salem, Oregon]] |[[Salem Armory Auditorium]] |- |January 9, 1992 | rowspan="4" |[[New York City]] |[[NBC Studios (New York City)|NBC Studios]] (''[[Saturday Night Live]]'') | rowspan="4" |<small>N/A</small> |- |January 10, 1992 |[[MTV Studios]] |- |January 11, 1992 | rowspan="2" |[[NBC Studios (New York City)|NBC Studios]] (''[[Saturday Night Live]]'') |- |January 11, 1992 |- ! colspan="5" |Oceania |- |January 24, 1992 | rowspan="2" |[[Sydney]] | rowspan="11" |[[Australia]] |[[Phoenician Club]] |[[The Meanies]] & [[Tumbleweed_(band)|Tumbleweed]] |- |January 25, 1992 |[[Big Day Out]] |Various Artists |- |January 26, 1992 |[[Gold Coast, Queensland|Gold Coast]] |Fisherman's Wharf | rowspan="2" |[[Violent Femmes]] |- |January 27, 1992 |[[Brisbane]] |[[Brisbane Festival Hall]] |- |January 30, 1992 |[[Adelaide]] |[[Thebarton Theatre]] |[[The Meanies]] & [[Tumbleweed_(band)|Tumbleweed]] |- | January 31, 1992 || rowspan="3" | [[Melbourne]] || rowspan="3" | [[The Palace (entertainment complex)|The Palace]] |[[Guttersnipes_(band)|Guttersnipes]] & [[Tumbleweed_(band)|Tumbleweed]] |- |February 1, 1992 |[[The Meanies]] & [[Tumbleweed_(band)|Tumbleweed]] |- |February 2, 1992 |[[Cosmic Psychos]] & [[Tumbleweed_(band)|Tumbleweed]] |- |February 5, 1992 |[[Canberra]] |[[Australian National University]] |[[Tumbleweed_(band)|Tumbleweed]] & The Village Idiots |- |February 6, 1992 | rowspan="2" |[[S