{{Infobox Newspaper | name = The Confidente Jump to: navigation, search | image = | caption = | type = Weekly | format = [[Broadsheet]] | foundation = 2011 | ceased publication = | price = NAD 5.00 | owners = | editor = [[Max Hamata]] | chiefeditor = | assoceditor = | maneditor = | staff = | language = English and Oshiwambo | political = | circulation = | headquarters = [[Windhoek West]] | sister newspapers = | oclc = | ISSN = | website = {{URL|www.confidente.com.na/}} }}
'''''The Confidente''''' is a weekly tabloid newspaper in Namibia.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.namibian.com.na/index.php?id=28&tx_ttnews%5Btt_news%5D=88071&no_cache=1|title=The Namibian|work=The Namibian|access-date=2018-07-18|language=en}}</ref> It was established by [[Max Hamata]] in 2011 as a weekly newspaper, it publishes in English.
